description:
The mix was recorded live on air at KTUH FM, January 17th, 2014. Last year was a pretty much amazing year for pop-oriented house and electro, so I went digging thru the year-end best-of lists and found plenty of tunes I'd slept on or simply not heard. Those ended up here, along with a couple of others that hadn't been on any of the other 808 mixes.
